      <title>我们命名摩根士丹利银行家领导主权财富基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/us-to-name-morgan-stanley-banker-to-lead-sovereign-wealth-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[商务部正在利用前摩根士丹利银行家迈克尔·格莱姆斯（Michael Grimes）领导计划的主权财富基金，这是唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统努力使美国对他认为对国家安全至关重要的项目的股份的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/us-to-name-morgan-stanley-banker-to-lead-sovereign-wealth-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 00:04:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对美国国际开发署的袭击的凌乱，解释说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/usaid-why-is-trump-attacking-it-what-are-the-effects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统及其政府效率沙皇埃隆·马斯克（Czar Elon Musk）对美国国际发展局（美国的马奎外国援助机构）发起了全面攻击。在第二任期的第一天，特朗普下令停止大多数外国援助，而马斯克后来威胁要完全关闭独立政府机构，认为这与美国的利益不符。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/usaid-why-is-trump-attacking-it-what-are-the-effects</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 23:42:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普目前向罢免举报人办公室的负责人清除了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/trump-cleared-by-court-to-oust-whistleblower-office-head-for-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦上诉法院为唐纳德·特朗普总统至少暂时解雇了一个独立的美国举报机构的负责人的道路，暂停了确定解雇是非法的法官的裁决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/trump-cleared-by-court-to-oust-whistleblower-office-head-for-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 23:38:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称为农业到加拿大的墨西哥关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/trump-weighs-agriculture-carveouts-from-canada-mexico-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统正在考虑将某些农产品免于对加拿大和墨西哥征收的关税，这是政府周三采取的最新举动，以减轻某些部门的新进口税款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/trump-weighs-agriculture-carveouts-from-canada-mexico-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 22:40:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国与爱尔兰的数据交易以提高能源安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/uk-strikes-data-deal-with-ireland-in-bid-to-lift-energy-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国和爱尔兰计划共享更多数据并削减繁文tape节，以提高能源安全，因为在脱欧后的紧张局势多年后，两个国家寻求更紧密的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/uk-strikes-data-deal-with-ireland-in-bid-to-lift-energy-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普警告哈马斯“地狱付款”，如果人质没有释放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/trump-warns-hamas-of-hell-to-pay-if-hostages-aren-t-released</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统警告哈马斯（Hamas），如果激进组织不立即在加沙释放人质，将会有“地狱”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/trump-warns-hamas-of-hell-to-pay-if-hostages-aren-t-released</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 22:21:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普国会的演讲获得了3660万观众，拜登的最高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/trump-s-speech-to-congress-draws-36-6-million-viewers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据尼尔森的评分，周二，超过3660万人观看了唐纳德·特朗普总统在国会联合会议上的讲话。这是总统在一月份上任第二任期后第一次讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/trump-s-speech-to-congress-draws-36-6-million-viewers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 22:18:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
